union all
select 'Intermediate' experiencestage, 5000 rankid
union all
select 'Experienced' experiencestage, 4000 rankid
union all
select 'Entry' experiencestage, 3000 rankid
union all

2000 as MATCHID
union all
select 'Match & Hired' as match_status,
1000 as MATCHID
union all
select 'No Match' as match_status,
3000 as MATCHID

model.pw_dbt_project.DIMSKILLLEVEL.name: DIMSKILLLEVEL
model.pw_dbt_project.DIMSKILLLEVEL.raw_code:
with data_level as 
(select 'Learning' as level, 1000 rankid
union all
select 'Beginner' as level, 2000 rankid
union all
select 'Entry' as level, 3000 rankid
union all
select 'Intermediate' as level, 4000 rankid
union all
select 'Expert' as level, 5000 rankid)
SELECT
sha2(ifnull(try_cast(upper(level) as varchar),'-99999999999999999')) as  id,
level as SKILLLEVELNAME,
null as SKILLLEVELID,
rankid
FROM data_level

model.pw_dbt_project.FACTEMPLOYERBILLING.name: FACTEMPLOYERBILLINGSUMMARY
model.pw_dbt_project.FACTEMPLOYERBILLING.raw_code:
select 
    sha2(ifnull(try_cast(accountid as varchar),'-99999999999999999') ||
    ifnull(try_cast(billingtype as varchar),'-99999999999999999') ||
    ifnull(try_cast(paymentmethodid as varchar),'-99999999999999999') ||
    ifnull(try_cast(paymentid as varchar),'-99999999999999999')) 
    as ID,
	AMOUNT,
    case billingtype when 'JOB' then
    (case BILLINGSUBTYPE when 'POST' then 'JOB_POST_PAYMENT'
                        when 'HIRE'  then ' JOB_HIRE_PAYMENT'
                        else null end)
                    when 'ACCESS_CODE' then 'ACCESS_CODE_BILLING'
                    when 'SERVICES' then
    (case BILLINGSUBTYPE when 'CAREER_SERVICE' then 'CAREER_SERVICE'
                        when 'WORK_FORCE_BUILDING'  then ' WORK_FORCE_BUILDING'
                        else null end)
                    else billingtype end
    NEW_BILLING_TYPE,
	BILLINGSUBTYPE,
	DESCRIPTION,
	EMPLOYERSERVICETRANSACTIONID,
	ENTITYID,
	ENTITYNAME,
    sha2(ifnull(
    case when billingtype = 'ACCESS_CODE' then ENTITYNAME else null end,'-99999999999999999'))  as ACCESSCODE,
    sha2(ifnull(try_cast(accountid as varchar),'-99999999999999999') ||
    ifnull(case when billingtype = 'JOB' then ENTITYNAME else null end,'-99999999999999999'))
    as JOB_ID,
	LASTUPDATED,
	LASTUPDATEDBY,
    PAYMENTDATE as PAYMENTDATETIME,
	to_date(PAYMENTDATE) PAYMENTDATE,
	PAYMENTSOURCE,
	RECEIPTNUMBER,
	RECEIPTTITLE,
	sha2(ifnull(try_cast(TALENTUSERID as varchar),'-99999999999999999')) TALENTUSERID,
	sha2(ifnull(try_cast(accountid as varchar),'-99999999999999999')) ACCOUNTID,
	BUCKET,
	BILLINGTYPE,
	PAYMENTMETHODID,
	PAYMENTID as ORG_PAYMENTREFERENCEID,
    sha2(ifnull(try_cast(accountid as varchar),'-99999999999999999') || ifnull(try_cast(    
    PAYMENTID as varchar),'-99999999999999999')) PAYMENTREFERENCEID
    from {{ref('stg_PAYMENTS_EMPLOYER_BILLING_SUMMARY')}} employer_billing_summary

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEMPLOYERACCOUN.name: ADMINEMPLOYERACCOUNTSTATUS
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEMPLOYERACCOUN.raw_code:
with inactive_no_days as 
(select value['value']::int as no_of_days from {{ref('stg_CONFIGURATION_STATIC_KEY_VALUES')}} static_key_values
where key = 'EMPLOYER_INACTIVE_NO_OF_DAYS')
select id, type, case when to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) < dateadd('DD',-1* inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date()) then true when ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date is null then true else false end inactive,
case when to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) < dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date()) and 
to_boolean(ACTIVITYSTATS['isanyserviceactive']) <> true then true
when ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date is null and to_boolean(ACTIVITYSTATS['isanyserviceactive']) <> true
then true
when (to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) >= dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date()) and
to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastjobcreateddate']::date) < dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date()) and
to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lasttransactiondate']::timestamp) < dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date()) and
to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastmatchdate']::date)  < dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date()) and 
to_boolean(ACTIVITYSTATS['isanyserviceactive']) <> true
and nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['activecmls']::int,0) > 0 ) then true
else false end churnstatus,
nullif(greatest(nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date,'0001-01-01'), nvl(to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastjobcreateddate']::date),'0001-01-01'),
nvl(to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lasttransactiondate']::timestamp),'0001-01-01'),
nvl(to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastmatchdate']::date),'0001-01-01')),'0001-01-01') lastactivitydate
--,ACTIVITYSTATS
from {{ref('FACTEMPLOYERACTIVITYSTATS')}} factemployeractivitystats 
join inactive_no_days 
on 1=1

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINTALENTJOBMATCH.name: ADMINTALENTJOBMATCHDETAILS
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINTALENTJOBMATCH.raw_code:
select tmp.id, tmp.userid, tmp.jobid, tmp.matchdate, tmp.score, tmp.stage, tmp.match_status, dimmatchstatus.match_status as derrived_match_status from (
select
sha2(ifnull(try_cast(facttalentuser.id as varchar),'-99999999999999999') || ifnull(try_cast( ifnull(ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH.match_status, 'No Match') as varchar),'-99999999999999999')) as  id
,
facttalentuser.id as userid,
ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH.jobid as jobid,
ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH.matchdate,
ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH.score,
ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH.stage,
ifnull(ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH.match_status, 'No Match') as match_status,
min(dimmatchstatus.matchid) over(partition by USERID) as min_matchid
from  {{ref('FACTTALENTUSER')}} facttalentuser
left outer join {{ref('ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH')}} adminemployerjobmatch
on facttalentuser.id = ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH.userid
join {{ref('DIMMATCHSTATUS')}} dimmatchstatus
on dimmatchstatus.match_status = ifnull(ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH.match_status, 'No Match')) tmp
join {{ref('DIMMATCHSTATUS')}} dimmatchstatus
on dimmatchstatus.matchid = tmp.min_matchid

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEDUCATORCOURSE.name: ADMINEDUCATORCOURSEMATCHES
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEDUCATORCOURSE.raw_code:
select factTalentCourseMatchCml.id,factTalentCourseMatchCml.userid,factTalentCourseMatchCml.courseid,factTalentCourseMatchCml.matchdate,factTalentCourseMatchCml.score, factTalentCourseMatchCml.stage, 
case when (matchdate is not null or score is not null) and lower(stage) <> 'enrolled' then 'Match but not Enrolled'
 when (matchdate is not null or score is not null) and lower(stage) = 'enrolled' then 'Match & Enrolled'
 else 'No Match' end as match_status
from  {{ref('FACTTALENTCOURSEMATCHCML')}} facttalentcoursematchcml
inner join {{ref('DIMEDUCATORACCOUNT')}} dimeducatoraccount on dimEducatorAccount.id = factTalentCourseMatchCml.accountid
left outer join {{ref('DIMCOUNTRY')}} dimcountry on dimCountry.id = factTalentCourseMatchCml.country
left outer join {{ref('FACTCOURSE')}} factcourse on factCourse.id = factTalentCourseMatchCml.courseid
where factCourse.status <> 'DRAFT' and (factCourse.enddate is null or factCourse.status <> 'ARCHIVE' or (factCourse.status = 'ARCHIVE' and factCourse.enddate >= dateadd('YYYY',-1,current_date())))

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMAT.name: ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCHSUMMARY
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMAT.raw_code:
select jobid, matchdate, match_status,array_to_string(array_distinct(job_skills),', ') job_skills,
array_to_string(array_distinct(must_job_skills),', ') must_job_skills from (
select factJob.id as jobid, min(ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH.matchdate) matchdate,
min(case when ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH.id is null then 3000 else (select min(matchid) 
from {{ref('DIMMATCHSTATUS')}} dimmatchstatus where match_status = ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH.match_status ) end) as matchid,
array_agg(ADMINEMPLOYERJOBSKILLS.skillname) job_skills,
array_agg(case when ADMINEMPLOYERJOBSKILLS.ismust = true then ADMINEMPLOYERJOBSKILLS.skillname end) must_job_skills
from {{ref('FACTJOB')}} factjob 
inner join {{ref('DIMJOB')}} dimjob 
on factJob.id = dimJob.id
left outer join {{ref('ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH')}} adminemployerjobmatch
on ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH.jobid = factjob.id
left outer join {{ref('ADMINEMPLOYERJOBSKILLS')}} adminemployerjobskills
on ADMINEMPLOYERJOBSKILLS.jobid = dimJob.id
where factjob.enddate is null or factjob.status <> 'ARCHIVE' or (factjob.status = 'ARCHIVE' and factjob.enddate >= dateadd('YYYY',-1,current_date()))
group by factJob.id) tmp
join {{ref('DIMMATCHSTATUS')}} dimmatchstatus on dimmatchstatus.matchid = tmp.matchid

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEMPLOYERSERVIC.name: ADMINEMPLOYERSERVICES
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEMPLOYERSERVIC.raw_code:
with module_types as 
(select upper(service) service from {{ref('DIMEMPLOYERSERVICES')}} dimemployerservices),
 valid_records as (
select factServicePurchaseHistory.service,factServicePurchaseHistory.entityid as accountid,factServicePurchaseHistory.contracttype,factServicePurchaseHistory.paymentfrequency,factServicePurchaseHistory.status,factServicePurchaseHistory.startdate,factServicePurchaseHistory.enddate   from {{ref('FACTSERVICEPURCHASEHISTORY')}} factservicepurchasehistory 
inner join {{ref('DIMEMPLOYERACCOUNT')}} dimemployeraccount
on dimemployeraccount.id = factservicepurchasehistory.entityid),
 invalid_records as (select service, id as accountid, 'PAY_AS_YOU_GO' contracttype, 'MONTHLY' paymentfrequency,'INACTIVE' status, null startdate, null enddate from {{ref('DIMEMPLOYERACCOUNT')}} dimemployeraccount, module_types
where not exists (select 1 from valid_records 
where valid_records.accountid = dimemployeraccount.id
and valid_records.service = module_types.service ))

select * from valid_records
union all
select * from invalid_records

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINTALENTMATCHSTA.raw_code:
with matched_talent as 
(select distinct userid from {{ref('ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH')}} adminemployerjobmatch)
select sha2(ifnull(try_cast(userid as varchar),'-99999999999999999') || ifnull(try_cast( match_status as varchar),'-99999999999999999')) as  id
,
userid, match_status from (
select userid, min(matchid) as matchid from (
select admintalent.id as userid, (select matchid from {{ref('DIMMATCHSTATUS')}} dimmatchstatus where match_status = 'No Match') as matchid 
from {{ref('ADMINTALENT')}} admintalent where not exists
(select 1 from matched_talent where admintalent.id = matched_talent.userid)
union all
select distinct userid, matchid from {{ref('ADMINEMPLOYERJOBMATCH')}} adminemployerjobmatch
join {{ref('DIMMATCHSTATUS')}} dimmatchstatus on dimmatchstatus.match_status = adminemployerjobmatch.match_status ) tmp group by userid
) tmp1 join {{ref('DIMMATCHSTATUS')}} dimmatchstatus on dimmatchstatus.matchid = tmp1.matchid

with revenue_per_session as
(select to_decimal(value['value']) as value 
from {{ref('stg_CONFIGURATION_STATIC_KEY_VALUES')}} static_key_values
where key = 'COACH_PER_SESSION_REVENUE' and activeflag = true)
select facttalentsession.id, 
facttalentsession.sessionid, 
facttalentsession.coachid as coachid, 
facttalentsession.scheduletime, 
initcap(lower(facttalentsession.status)) as status,
case when factAccessCodeTalentCoachingSession.id is null then false else true end accesscodeused,
count(distinct facttalentsession.id) * revenue_per_session.value as sessionCost,
facttalentsession.userid
from {{ref('FACTTALENTSESSION')}} facttalentsession
join revenue_per_session
on 1=1
left outer join {{ref('FACTTALENTCOACHINGPURCHASE')}} facttalentcoachingpurchase
on facttalentcoachingpurchase.talentsessionid = facttalentsession.talentsessionid
left outer join {{ref('FACTACCESSCODETALENTCOACHINGSESSION')}} factaccesscodetalentcoachingsession
on factAccessCodeTalentCoachingSession.talentsessionid = facttalentsession.talentsessionid
where scheduletime >= dateadd('YYYY',-1, current_date())
group by facttalentsession.id, 
facttalentsession.sessionid, 
facttalentsession.coachid, 
facttalentsession.scheduletime, 
facttalentsession.status,
facttalentsession.talentsessionid,
factAccessCodeTalentCoachingSession.id,
revenue_per_session.value,
facttalentsession.userid

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEDUCATORACCOUN.name: ADMINEDUCATORACCOUNTSTATUS
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEDUCATORACCOUN.raw_code:
with inactive_no_days as 
(select value['value']::int as no_of_days from {{ref('stg_CONFIGURATION_STATIC_KEY_VALUES')}} static_key_values
where key = 'EDUCATOR_INACTIVE_NO_OF_DAYS')
select id, type, case 
when to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) < dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date()) then true
when ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date is null then true else false end inactive,
case 
when (to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) < dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date()) and ACTIVITYSTATS['hasactivecourse']::boolean <> true) then true 
when (to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) is null and 
ACTIVITYSTATS['hasactivecourse']::boolean <> true) then true 
when to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) >= dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date()) and
ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date is not null and
ACTIVITYSTATS['lastcoursecreateddate']::date < dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date())
and ACTIVITYSTATS['lastmatchdatethen']::date < dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date()) then true
else false end churnstatus,
nullif(greatest(nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date,'0001-01-01'), nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastcoursecreateddate']::date,'0001-01-01'),
nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastmatchdate']::date,'0001-01-01')),'0001-01-01')
 lastactivitydate
from {{ref('FACTEDUCATORACTIVITYSTATS')}} facteducatoractivitystats
join inactive_no_days 
on 1=1

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINACCOUNTSTATUS.name: ADMINACCOUNTSTATUS
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINACCOUNTSTATUS.raw_code:
select id, type, case when to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) < dateadd('DD',-90,current_date()) then true when ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date is null then true else false end inactive,
case when to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) < dateadd('DD',-90,current_date()) and 
to_boolean(ACTIVITYSTATS['isanyserviceactive']) <> true then true
when ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date is null and to_boolean(ACTIVITYSTATS['isanyserviceactive']) <> true
then true
when (to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) >= dateadd('DD',-90,current_date()) and
to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastjobcreateddate']::date) < dateadd('DD',-90,current_date()) and
to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lasttransactiondate']::timestamp) < dateadd('DD',-90,current_date()) and
to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastmatchdate']::date)  < dateadd('DD',-90,current_date()) and 
to_boolean(ACTIVITYSTATS['isanyserviceactive']) <> true) then true
else false end churnstatus,
nullif(greatest(nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date,'0001-01-01'), nvl(to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastjobcreateddate']::date),'0001-01-01'),
nvl(to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lasttransactiondate']::timestamp),'0001-01-01'),
nvl(to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastmatchdate']::date),'0001-01-01')),'0001-01-01') lastactivitydate
--,ACTIVITYSTATS
from {{ref('FACTEMPLOYERACTIVITYSTATS')}} factemployeractivitystats
union all
select id, type, case 
when to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) < dateadd('DD',-90,current_date()) then true
when ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date is null then true
when ACTIVITYSTATS['accountstatus']::varchar <> 'Active' then true else false end inactive,
case 
when (to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) < dateadd('DD',-90,current_date()) and ACTIVITYSTATS['hasactivepaidsubscription']::boolean <> false) then true 
when (ACTIVITYSTATS['accountstatus']::varchar <> 'Active' 
and ACTIVITYSTATS['hasactivepaidsubscription']::boolean <> false) then true
when to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) >= dateadd('DD',-90,current_date()) and
    ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date is not null and
    ACTIVITYSTATS['hasactivepaidsubscription']::boolean <> true 
and (ACTIVITYSTATS['lastitempurchasedate']::date is null or
ACTIVITYSTATS['lastitempurchasedate']::date < dateadd('DD',-90,current_date())) then true
else false end churnstatus,
nullif(greatest(nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastitempurchasedate']::date,'0001-01-01'), nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date,'0001-01-01')),'0001-01-01') lastactivitydate
--, activitystats
from {{ref('FACTTALENTACTIVITYSTATS')}} facttalentactivitystats 
--limit 100 

--select to_date('2023-12-02 00:13:02.833')

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINTALENTACCESSCO.raw_code:
with job_match_history_skilling as
(select id from (
select id, developtag from {{ref('FACTJOBMATCHAML')}} factjobmatchaml
where lower(developtag) = 'skilling'
union 
select id, developtag from {{ref('FACTJOBMATCHAMLHISTORY')}} factjobmatchamlhistory
where lower(developtag) = 'skilling') tmp
 group by id),
matched_access_code_details as (
select factjobmatchdetail.id, userid, jobid, accountid, matchdate, factaccesscode.id as accesscode, packageeffectivefrom as startdate, least(expirydate, ifnull(deactivateddate,expirydate)) as enddate
from {{ref('FACTJOBMATCHDETAIL')}} factjobmatchdetail
join {{ref('FACTACCESSCODE')}} factaccesscode on factaccesscode.id = matchedaccesscode),
talent_course_match_completions as
(select id, userid, courseid, matchdate from {{ref('FACTTALENTCOURSEMATCHCML')}} facttalentcoursematchcml
where lower(stage) = 'completed'),
talent_access_code_redumption as
(select accesscode, userid, redeemeddate, 
lead(redeemeddate) over(partition by userid order by redeemeddate) next_redeemeddate
from {{ref('FACTTALENTACCESSCODEREDUMPTIONDATA')}} facttalentaccesscoderedumptiondata)


select matched_access_code_details.id, matched_access_code_details.jobid, matched_access_code_details.accountid, matched_access_code_details.accesscode, matched_access_code_details.userid from job_match_history_skilling
join matched_access_code_details
on matched_access_code_details.id = job_match_history_skilling.id
join talent_course_match_completions
on talent_course_match_completions.userid = matched_access_code_details.userid
join talent_access_code_redumption
on talent_access_code_redumption.userid = matched_access_code_details.userid
and talent_access_code_redumption.accesscode = matched_access_code_details.accesscode
join {{ref('FACTJOB')}} factjob on factjob.id = matched_access_code_details.jobid
where matched_access_code_details.matchdate between talent_access_code_redumption.redeemeddate
and least(matched_access_code_details.enddate,ifnull(talent_access_code_redumption.next_redeemeddate,matched_access_code_details.enddate))
and talent_course_match_completions.matchdate between talent_access_code_redumption.redeemeddate
and least(matched_access_code_details.enddate,ifnull(talent_access_code_redumption.next_redeemeddate,matched_access_code_details.enddate))
and factjob.enddate is null or factjob.status <> 'ARCHIVE' or (factjob.status = 'ARCHIVE' and factjob.enddate >= dateadd('YYYY',-1,current_date()))

model.pw_dbt_project.FACTTALENTACTIVITYS.name: FACTTALENTACTIVITYSTATS
model.pw_dbt_project.FACTTALENTACTIVITYS.raw_code:
select 'talent' as type, userid as id, 
object_construct_keep_null('lastlogindate',lastlogindate,
'lastitempurchasedate', lastitempurchasedate,
'lastsubscriptionpurchasedate', lastsubscriptionpurchasedate,
'lastpaidsubscriptionpurchasedate', lastpaidsubscriptionpurchasedate,
'hasactivesubscription', hasactivesubscription,
'hasactivepaidsubscription', hasactivepaidsubscription,
'activepaidsubscriptions', activepaidsubscriptions,
'accountstatus', status,
'lastprofileupdateddate',lastprofileupdateddate,
'lastjobmatcheddate', lastjobmatcheddate,
'lastcoursematcheddate', lastcoursematcheddate,
'lastskillsupdateddate', lastskillsupdateddate
) as activitystats
from (
select tu.id as userid, max(u.status) status, max(lastlogindate) lastlogindate,
max(tpi.purchaseddate) lastitempurchasedate,
max(case when tpi.purchasetype = 'Subscription' then tpi.purchaseddate else null end) lastsubscriptionpurchasedate,
max(case when tpi.purchasetype = 'Subscription' and sp.memberlevel=2 then tpi.purchaseddate else null end) lastpaidsubscriptionpurchasedate,
max(case when tpi.purchasetype = 'Subscription' and add_months(tpi.purchaseddate,sp.durationmonths) > current_date then true else false end) hasactivesubscription,
max(case when tpi.purchasetype = 'Subscription' and sp.memberlevel=2 and add_months(tpi.purchaseddate,sp.durationmonths) > current_date then true else false end) hasactivepaidsubscription,
array_unique_agg(case when tpi.purchasetype = 'Subscription' and sp.memberlevel=2 and add_months(tpi.purchaseddate,sp.durationmonths) > current_date then sp.name else null end) as activepaidsubscriptions,
max(tap.lastupdated) as lastprofileupdateddate,
max(jmd.matchdate) as lastjobmatcheddate,
max(tcm.matchdate) as lastcoursematcheddate,
max(ts.lastupdated) as lastskillsupdateddate

from {{ref('FACTTALENTUSER')}} tu
join {{ref('DIMUSER')}} u
on u.id = tu.id
left outer join {{ref('FACTTALENTPURCHASEITEMS')}} tpi
on tpi.userid = tu.id
left outer join {{ref('DIMSUBSCRIPTIONPLAN')}} sp
on sp.id = tpi.subscriptionid
and sp.plantype = 'Talent'
left outer join {{ref('FACTTALENTACCOUNTPROFILE')}} tap
on tap.id = tu.id
left outer join {{ref('FACTJOBMATCHDETAIL')}} jmd
on jmd.userid = tu.id
left outer join {{ref('FACTTALENTCOURSEMATCHCML')}} tcm
on tcm.userid = tu.id
left outer join {{ref('FACTTALENTSKILLS')}} ts
on ts.userid = tu.id
group by tu.id
) tmp

model.pw_dbt_project.FACTEMPLOYERACTIVIT.name: FACTEMPLOYERACTIVITYSTATS
model.pw_dbt_project.FACTEMPLOYERACTIVIT.raw_code:
select 'employer' as type, accountid as id, object_construct_keep_null('lastlogindate', lastlogindate,
'lastjobcreateddate',lastjobcreateddate,
'hasactivejob',hasactivejob,
'activejobs', activejobs,
'lastmatchdate', lastmatchdate,
'jobmatchcount', jobmatchcount,
'lasttransactiondate',lasttransactiondate,
'isanyserviceactive',isanyserviceactive,
'activeservices',activeservices,
'activecmls', activecmls) as activitystats from (
select ea.id as accountid, max(lastlogindate) lastlogindate,
max(j.createdate) lastjobcreateddate,
max(case when j.status = 'ACTIVE' then true else false end) hasactivejob,
sum(case when j.status = 'ACTIVE' then 1 else 0 end) activejobs,
max(et.transactiondate) lasttransactiondate,
max(jmd.matchdate) lastmatchdate,
count(distinct jmd.jobid) jobmatchcount,
max(case when least(ifnull(sph.deactivateddate,sph.enddate), sph.enddate) > current_date then false else true end) isanyserviceactive,
array_unique_agg(case when least(ifnull(sph.deactivateddate,sph.enddate), sph.enddate) > current_date then es.service else null end) activeservices,
sum(case when jma.stage <> 'Hired' then 0 else 1 end) as activecmls
from {{ref('DIMEMPLOYERACCOUNT')}}  ea
left outer join {{ref('FACTEMPLOYERUSER')}}  eu
on eu.accountid = ea.id
left outer join {{ref('FACTJOB')}} j
on j.accountid = ea.id
left outer join {{ref('FACTJOBMATCHDETAIL')}} jmd
on jmd.jobid = j.id
left outer join {{ref('FACTEMPLOYERTRANSACTIONS')}} et
on et.accountid = ea.id
left outer join {{ref('FACTSERVICEPURCHASEHISTORY')}} sph
on sph.entityid = ea.id
left outer join {{ref('DIMEMPLOYERSERVICES')}} es
on es.id = sph.serviceid
left outer join {{ref('FACTJOBMATCHAML')}} jma
on jma.accountid = ea.id
and jma.jobid = j.id

group by ea.id) tmp

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEDUCATORCOURSE.name: ADMINEDUCATORCOURSEMATCHDETAILS
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEDUCATORCOURSE.raw_code:
select factTalentCourseMatchCml.userid,factCourse.id 
 as courseid,factTalentCourseMatchCml.matchdate,factTalentCourseMatchCml.score, factTalentCourseMatchCml.stage, 
case when factTalentCourseMatchCml.id is null then 'No Match' when (matchdate is not null or score is not null) and lower(stage) <> 'enrolled' then 'Match but not Enrolled'
 when (matchdate is not null or score is not null) and lower(stage) = 'enrolled' then 'Match & Enrolled'
 else 'No Match' end as match_status,
array_to_string(array_agg(aoi.areaofinterestname),',') talentareasofinterest
from  {{ref('FACTCOURSE')}} factcourse 
inner join {{ref('DIMEDUCATORACCOUNT')}} dimeducatoraccount 
on dimEducatorAccount.id = factCourse.accountid
left outer join {{ref('DIMCOUNTRY')}} dimcountry 
on dimCountry.id = factCourse.country
left outer join {{ref('FACTTALENTCOURSEMATCHCML')}} facttalentcoursematchcml 
on factCourse.id = factTalentCourseMatchCml.courseid 
left outer join {{ref('ADMINTALENTAREASOFINTEREST')}} aoi
on aoi.userid = facttalentcoursematchcml.userid
where factCourse.status <> 'DRAFT' and (factCourse.enddate is null or factCourse.status <> 'ARCHIVE' or (factCourse.status = 'ARCHIVE' and factCourse.enddate >= dateadd('YYYY',-1,current_date())))
group by factTalentCourseMatchCml.id,factTalentCourseMatchCml.userid,factCourse.id,factTalentCourseMatchCml.matchdate,factTalentCourseMatchCml.score, factTalentCourseMatchCml.stage

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINTALENTTRANSACT.name: ADMINTALENTTRANSACTIONS
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINTALENTTRANSACT.raw_code:
select tpi.id, 
userid, 
tpi.amount, 
case when purchasetype = 'Subscription' then upper(sp.roleid) else featurekey end as item, 
count as item_count,
purchaseddate,
purchasetype,
case sp.memberlevel when  2 then 'PAID' when null then 'NA' else 'FREE' end issubscriptionpaid,
sp.durationmonths plandurationinmonths,
case sp.memberlevel when  2 then
tpi.amount/(case plandurationinmonths when null then 1.0 when 0 then 1.0 else plandurationinmonths end)
else 0 end MONTHLYRECURRINGREVENUE,
case sp.memberlevel when 2 then add_months(purchaseddate, plandurationinmonths) else null end expirydate
from {{ref('FACTTALENTPURCHASEITEMS')}} tpi
left outer join {{ref('DIMSUBSCRIPTIONPLAN')}}  sp
on sp.id = tpi.subscriptionplanid
and sp.plantype = 'Talent'
where purchaseddate >= dateadd('YYYY',-1,current_date())

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINTALENTACCOUNTS.name: ADMINTALENTACCOUNTSTATUS
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINTALENTACCOUNTS.raw_code:
with inactive_no_days as 
(select value['value']::int as no_of_days from {{ref('stg_CONFIGURATION_STATIC_KEY_VALUES')}} static_key_values
where key = 'TALENT_INACTIVE_NO_OF_DAYS')
select tas.id, type, case 
when to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) < dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date()) then true
when ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date is null then true
when ACTIVITYSTATS['accountstatus']::varchar <> 'Active' then true else false end inactive,
case 
when to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) < dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date()) then true 
when ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date is null then true
when ACTIVITYSTATS['accountstatus']::varchar <> 'Active' then true
when to_date(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date) >= dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date()) and
    ACTIVITYSTATS['hasactivepaidsubscription']::boolean <> true 
and nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastitempurchasedate']::date,'0001-01-01') < dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date())
and nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastprofileupdateddate']::date,'0001-01-01') < dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date())
and nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastjobmatcheddate']::date,'0001-01-01') < dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date())
and nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastcoursematcheddate']::date,'0001-01-01') < dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date())
and nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastskillsupdateddate']::date,'0001-01-01') < dateadd('DD',-1*inactive_no_days.no_of_days,current_date())
then true
else false end churnstatus,
nullif(greatest(nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastitempurchasedate']::date,'0001-01-01'), nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastlogindate']::date,'0001-01-01'),nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastprofileupdateddate']::date,'0001-01-01'), nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastjobmatcheddate']::date,'0001-01-01'),
nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastcoursematcheddate']::date,'0001-01-01'),
nvl(ACTIVITYSTATS['lastskillsupdateddate']::date,'0001-01-01')),'0001-01-01') lastactivitydate
--, activitystats
from {{ref('FACTTALENTACTIVITYSTATS')}} tas
join {{ref('FACTTALENTUSER')}} tu
on tu.id = tas.id
join  {{ref('DIMUSER')}} u
on u.id = tu.id
join inactive_no_days 
on 1=1
where u.status = 'Active'

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEDUCATORTRANSA.name: ADMINEDUCATORTRANSACTIONS
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEDUCATORTRANSA.raw_code:

on EA.id =  EBD.accountid

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEMPLOYERACCESS.name: ADMINEMPLOYERACCESSCODESUMMARY
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEMPLOYERACCESS.raw_code:
select face.accountid,fac.status, count(distinct fac.accesscode) unique_accesscode_count, count(1) as row_count, count(distinct tu.id) assigned_talent_count
from {{ref('FACTACCESSCODEEMPLOYER')}} face
join {{ref('DIMACCESSCODE')}} fac
on fac.id= face.accesscode
join {{ref('FACTACCESSCODE')}} ffac

--join pw_dwh_prod.fact.factaccesscodeusagerecord facur

model.pw_dbt_project.FACTEDUCATORACTIVIT.name: FACTEDUCATORACTIVITYSTATS
model.pw_dbt_project.FACTEDUCATORACTIVIT.raw_code:
select 'educator' as type, 
accountid as id, 
object_construct_keep_null('lastlogindate', lastlogindate,
'lastcoursecreateddate', lastcoursecreateddate,
'hasactivecourse', hasactivecourse,
'activecourses', activecourses,
'lastmatchdate', lastmatchdate,
'interestedtalents', interestedtalent,
'numberofcoursematched', numberofcoursematched,
'numberofuniquematchedtalent', numberofuniquematchedtalent) as activitystats from (
select ed.id as accountid,
max(lastlogindate) lastlogindate,
max(c.createdate) lastcoursecreateddate,
max(case when c.status = 'ACTIVE' then true else false end) hasactivecourse,
sum(case when c.status = 'ACTIVE' then 1 else 0 end) activecourses,
max(tcm.matchdate) lastmatchdate,
sum(case when tcm.stage = 'INTERESTED' then 1 else 0 end) interestedtalent,
count(distinct tcm.courseid) numberofcoursematched,
count(distinct tcm.userid) numberofuniquematchedtalent
from {{ref('DIMEDUCATORACCOUNT')}} ed
left outer join {{ref('FACTEDUCATORUSER')}} eu
on eu.accountid = ed.id
left outer join {{ref('FACTCOURSE')}} c
on c.accountid = ed.id
left outer join {{ref('FACTTALENTCOURSEMATCHCML')}} tcm
on tcm.accountid = ed.id
and tcm.courseid = c.id
group by ed.id) tmp

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEMPLOYERTRANSA.name: ADMINEMPLOYERTRANSACTIONS
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEMPLOYERTRANSA.raw_code:
select et.id, et.accountid, et.jobid, et.accesscode as accesscodeid, initcap(billingtype) billingtype, 
et.amount, et.paymentdate, paymentmethod,
et.paymentstatus, ea.accountname, ac.accesscode, j.jobtitle, c.companyname,
case when es.id is null then false else true end revenuefrommodulepurchase,
initcap(sph.CONTRACTTYPE) CONTRACTTYPE,
initcap(sph.PAYMENTFREQUENCY) PAYMENTFREQUENCY,
case when upper(CONTRACTTYPE) in ('ONE_YEAR', 'THREE_YEAR')
then (
case upper(paymentfrequency)
    when 'MONTHLY' then et.amount
    when 'QUARTERLY' then et.amount/4.0
    when 'YEARLY' then et.amount/12.0 end) else 0 end as MONTHLYRECURRINGREVENUE,
add_months(paymentdate, (case upper(paymentfrequency)
    when 'MONTHLY' then 1
    when 'QUARTERLY' then 4
    when 'YEARLY' then 12 end)) as EXPIRYDATE
from {{ref('FACTEMPLOYERTRANSACTIONS')}} et
left outer join {{ref('DIMEMPLOYERACCOUNT')}} ea
on ea.id = et.accountid
left outer join {{ref('DIMACCESSCODE')}} ac
on ac.id = et.accesscode
left outer join {{ref('DIMJOB')}} j
on j.id = et.jobid
left outer join {{ref('FACTJOB')}} fj
on fj.id = et.jobid
left outer join {{ref('DIMCOMPANY')}} c
on c.id = fj.companyid
left outer join {{ref('DIMEMPLOYERSERVICES')}} es
on upper(es.service) = upper(et.billingtype)
left outer join {{ref('FACTEMPLOYERSERVICETRANSACTIONS')}} est
on est.paymentreferenceid = et.paymentreferenceid
left outer join {{ref('FACTSERVICEPURCHASEHISTORY')}} sph
--on sph.entityid = et.accountid
on sph.id = est.servicepurchasehistoryid
--and sph.paymentreferenceid = et.paymentreferenceid
where paymentdate >= dateadd('YYYY',-1, current_date())

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINTALENT.name: ADMINTALENT
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINTALENT.raw_code:
select factTalentUser.id,dimUser.userid, replace(to_varchar(dimUser.fullname['firstname']),'"','') as firstname,replace(to_varchar(dimUser.fullname['lastname']),'"','') as lastname,dimUser.status,max(factuseremails.email) email, array_agg(factuseremails.email) emailAll, factTalentAccountProfile.city,initcap(ifnull(factTalentAccountProfile.experiencestage,'Unknown')) experiencestage,dimCountry.name as countryname,dimCountry.code as countrycode
,ifnull(experiencestages.rankid,0) experiencestage_rank, facttalentuser.registrationdate
from  {{ref('FACTTALENTUSER')}} facttalentuser
inner join {{ref('DIMUSER')}} dimuser on dimUser.id = factTalentUser.id

left outer join {{ref('DIMCOUNTRY')}} dimcountry on dimCountry.id = factTalentAccountProfile.country
left outer join {{ref('FACTUSEREMAILS')}} factuseremails on factuseremails.id = dimUser.id

	'' LASTNAME,

    a.rankid as experiencestage_rank,

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEDUCATORCOURSE.name: ADMINEDUCATORCOURSEMATCHSUMMARY
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINEDUCATORCOURSE.raw_code:
with matching_states as
(select 3000 as rank, 'Match & Enrolled' status
union all
select 2000 as rank,'Match but not Enrolled' status
union all
select 1000 as rank, 'No Match' status)
select courseid, lastmatchdate, ms.status as match_status from (
select courseid, max(matchdate) as lastmatchdate,
max(ms.rank) as net_rank
from {{ref('ADMINEDUCATORCOURSEMATCHDETAILS')}} ecmd
join matching_states ms
on ms.status = ecmd.match_status
group by courseid) tmp
join matching_states ms
on ms.rank = tmp.net_rank

model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINCOACHTALENTSES.name: ADMINCOACHTALENTSESSION
model.pw_dbt_project.ADMINCOACHTALENTSES.raw_code:
with revenue_per_session as
(select to_decimal(value['value']) as value 
from {{ref('stg_CONFIGURATION_STATIC_KEY_VALUES')}} static_key_values
where key = 'COACH_PER_SESSION_REVENUE' and activeflag = true)
select facttalentsession.id, 
facttalentsession.sessionid, 
facttalentsession.coachid as coachid, 
facttalentsession.scheduletime, 
initcap(lower(facttalentsession.status)) as status,
case when factAccessCodeTalentCoachingSession.id is null then false else true end accesscodeused,
case when ifnull(ifnull(nullif(facttalentcoachingpurchase.baseamount,0),factaccesscodefeaturecost.featurecost),0) > 0 then 
count(distinct facttalentsession.id) * revenue_per_session.value else 0 end as sessionCost,
count(distinct facttalentsession.id) * ifnull(ifnull(nullif(facttalentcoachingpurchase.baseamount,0),factaccesscodefeaturecost.featurecost),0) sessionRevenue,
facttalentsession.userid
from {{ref('FACTTALENTSESSION')}} facttalentsession
join revenue_per_session
on 1=1
left outer join {{ref('FACTTALENTCOACHINGPURCHASE')}} facttalentcoachingpurchase
on facttalentcoachingpurchase.talentsessionid = facttalentsession.talentsessionid
and facttalentcoachingpurchase.status = 'PAID'
left outer join {{ref('FACTACCESSCODETALENTCOACHINGSESSION')}} as factaccesscodetalentcoachingsession
on factaccesscodetalentcoachingsession.talentsessionid = facttalentsession.talentsessionid
left outer join {{ref('FACTACCESSCODEFEATURECOST')}} factaccesscodefeaturecost
on factaccesscodefeaturecost.accesscode = factaccesscodetalentcoachingsession.accesscode
and factaccesscodefeaturecost.featurekey = 'COACHING_SESSION'
where scheduletime >= dateadd('YYYY',-1, current_date())
group by facttalentsession.id, 
facttalentsession.sessionid, 
facttalentsession.coachid, 
facttalentsession.scheduletime, 
facttalentsession.status,
facttalentsession.talentsessionid,
factAccessCodeTalentCoachingSession.id,

macro.dbt_snowflake.snowflake__get_catal.macro_sql:
{% macro snowflake__get_catalog(information_schema, schemas) -%}
  {% set query %}
      with tables as (

          select
              table_catalog as "table_database",
              table_schema as "table_schema",
              table_name as "table_name",
              coalesce(table_type, 'DYNAMIC TABLE') as "table_type",
              comment as "table_comment",

              -- note: this is the _role_ that owns the table
              table_owner as "table_owner",

              'Clustering Key' as "stats:clustering_key:label",
              clustering_key as "stats:clustering_key:value",
              'The key used to cluster this table' as "stats:clustering_key:description",
              (clustering_key is not null) as "stats:clustering_key:include",

              'Row Count' as "stats:row_count:label",
              row_count as "stats:row_count:value",
              'An approximate count of rows in this table' as "stats:row_count:description",
              (row_count is not null) as "stats:row_count:include",

              'Approximate Size' as "stats:bytes:label",
              bytes as "stats:bytes:value",
              'Approximate size of the table as reported by Snowflake' as "stats:bytes:description",
              (bytes is not null) as "stats:bytes:include",

              'Last Modified' as "stats:last_modified:label",
              to_varchar(convert_timezone('UTC', last_altered), 'yyyy-mm-dd HH24:MI'||'UTC') as "stats:last_modified:value",
              'The timestamp for last update/change' as "stats:last_modified:description",
              (last_altered is not null and table_type='BASE TABLE') as "stats:last_modified:include"

          from {{ information_schema }}.tables
          where (
            {%- for schema in schemas -%}
              upper("table_schema") = upper('{{ schema }}'){%- if not loop.last %} or {% endif -%}
            {%- endfor -%}
          )

      ),

      columns as (

          select
              table_catalog as "table_database",
              table_schema as "table_schema",
              table_name as "table_name",

              column_name as "column_name",
              ordinal_position as "column_index",
              data_type as "column_type",
              comment as "column_comment"

          from {{ information_schema }}.columns
          where (
            {%- for schema in schemas -%}
              upper("table_schema") = upper('{{ schema }}'){%- if not loop.last %} or {% endif -%}
            {%- endfor -%}
          )
      )

      select *
      from tables
      join columns using ("table_database", "table_schema", "table_name")
      order by "column_index"
    {%- endset -%}

  {{ return(run_query(query)) }}

{%- endmacro %}

macro.dbt.default__snapshot_staging_tabl.macro_sql:
{% macro default__snapshot_staging_table(strategy, source_sql, target_relation) -%}

    with snapshot_query as (

        {{ source_sql }}

    ),

    snapshotted_data as (

        select *,
            {{ strategy.unique_key }} as dbt_unique_key

        from {{ target_relation }}
        where dbt_valid_to is null

    ),

    insertions_source_data as (

        select
            *,
            {{ strategy.unique_key }} as dbt_unique_key,
            {{ strategy.updated_at }} as dbt_updated_at,
            {{ strategy.updated_at }} as dbt_valid_from,
            nullif({{ strategy.updated_at }}, {{ strategy.updated_at }}) as dbt_valid_to,
            {{ strategy.scd_id }} as dbt_scd_id

        from snapshot_query
    ),

    updates_source_data as (

        select
            *,
            {{ strategy.unique_key }} as dbt_unique_key,
            {{ strategy.updated_at }} as dbt_updated_at,
            {{ strategy.updated_at }} as dbt_valid_from,
            {{ strategy.updated_at }} as dbt_valid_to

        from snapshot_query
    ),

    {%- if strategy.invalidate_hard_deletes %}

    deletes_source_data as (

        select
            *,
            {{ strategy.unique_key }} as dbt_unique_key
        from snapshot_query
    ),
    {% endif %}

    insertions as (

        select
            'insert' as dbt_change_type,
            source_data.*

        from insertions_source_data as source_data
        left outer join snapshotted_data on snapshotted_data.dbt_unique_key = source_data.dbt_unique_key
        where snapshotted_data.dbt_unique_key is null
           or (
                snapshotted_data.dbt_unique_key is not null
            and (
                {{ strategy.row_changed }}
            )
        )

    ),

    updates as (

        select
            'update' as dbt_change_type,
            source_data.*,
            snapshotted_data.dbt_scd_id

        from updates_source_data as source_data
        join snapshotted_data on snapshotted_data.dbt_unique_key = source_data.dbt_unique_key
        where (
            {{ strategy.row_changed }}
        )
    )

    {%- if strategy.invalidate_hard_deletes -%}
    ,

    deletes as (

        select
            'delete' as dbt_change_type,
            source_data.*,
            {{ snapshot_get_time() }} as dbt_valid_from,
            {{ snapshot_get_time() }} as dbt_updated_at,
            {{ snapshot_get_time() }} as dbt_valid_to,
            snapshotted_data.dbt_scd_id

        from snapshotted_data
        left join deletes_source_data as source_data on snapshotted_data.dbt_unique_key = source_data.dbt_unique_key
        where source_data.dbt_unique_key is null
    )
    {%- endif %}

    select * from insertions
    union all
    select * from updates
    {%- if strategy.invalidate_hard_deletes %}
    union all
    select * from deletes
    {%- endif %}

{%- endmacro %}

macro.dbt.default__snapshot_merge_sql.macro_sql:
{% macro default__snapshot_merge_sql(target, source, insert_cols) -%}
    {%- set insert_cols_csv = insert_cols | join(', ') -%}

    merge into {{ target }} as DBT_INTERNAL_DEST
    using {{ source }} as DBT_INTERNAL_SOURCE
    on DBT_INTERNAL_SOURCE.dbt_scd_id = DBT_INTERNAL_DEST.dbt_scd_id

    when matched
     and DBT_INTERNAL_DEST.dbt_valid_to is null
     and DBT_INTERNAL_SOURCE.dbt_change_type in ('update', 'delete')
        then update
        set dbt_valid_to = DBT_INTERNAL_SOURCE.dbt_valid_to

    when not matched
     and DBT_INTERNAL_SOURCE.dbt_change_type = 'insert'
        then insert ({{ insert_cols_csv }})
        values ({{ insert_cols_csv }})

{% endmacro %}

doc.dbt.__overview__.block_contents:
### Welcome!

Welcome to the auto-generated documentation for your dbt project!

### Navigation

You can use the `Project` and `Database` navigation tabs on the left side of the window to explore the models
in your project.

#### Project Tab
The `Project` tab mirrors the directory structure of your dbt project. In this tab, you can see all of the
models defined in your dbt project, as well as models imported from dbt packages.

#### Database Tab
The `Database` tab also exposes your models, but in a format that looks more like a database explorer. This view
shows relations (tables and views) grouped into database schemas. Note that ephemeral models are _not_ shown
in this interface, as they do not exist in the database.

### Graph Exploration
You can click the blue icon on the bottom-right corner of the page to view the lineage graph of your models.

On model pages, you'll see the immediate parents and children of the model you're exploring. By clicking the `Expand`
button at the top-right of this lineage pane, you'll be able to see all of the models that are used to build,
or are built from, the model you're exploring.

Once expanded, you'll be able to use the `--select` and `--exclude` model selection syntax to filter the
models in the graph. For more information on model selection, check out the [dbt docs](https://docs.getdbt.com/docs/model-selection-syntax).

Note that you can also right-click on models to interactively filter and explore the graph.
